## forms

since
: 1.0.0

arguments
: `$prefix`: `$prefix-form` *[string]*: this is added to the beginning of selectors.


Add all the marscss forms class.

~~~scss
@include style(forms());
~~~


## customize forms

There is a set of variables in default-variable that allow you to modify some properties of these mixins and not have to rewrite them for small adjustments

<%= code_snippet('forms',
